128
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,900
-¿Entonces de qué me encargaré yo?

129
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:58,100
-Para ti, Lunch, para ti no tengo nada.

130
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:28,500
