165
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,260
Perdona.

166
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:54,600
No, da igual.

167
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,720
Escucha, Colette, yo...

168
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,380
¿Ah?

169
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:10,300
